---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Dr. Carie Perrino, NMD, RDN, CLT · Love Your Health Natural Medicine" description="Meet Dr. Carie Perrino — naturopathic doctor, registered dietitian, Sonoran University faculty, and co-founder of Love Your Health Natural Medicine in Tempe, AZ.">

  <!-- ==================== 1. BIO HERO ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-cream relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[60rem] h-[60rem] rounded-full bg-[#F5E0D0]/20 blur-[140px] -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-0">

          <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-5 relative overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/images/doctors/team-photo.jpg" alt="Dr. Carie Perrino, NMD, RDN, CLT — Co-Founder of Love Your Health Natural Medicine" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top min-h-[300px]" loading="eager" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-charcoal/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            <span class="absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-terracotta text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Co-Founder</span>
          </div>

          <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-7 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="hero-el mb-4">
              <a href="/doctors" class="text-xs text-text-light hover:text-sage transition-colors">Doctors</a>
              <span class="text-xs text-text-light/40 mx-1.5">/</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-terracotta font-semibold">Dr. Perrino</span>
            </nav>

            <h1 class="hero-el text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3rem)] font-black text-charcoal mb-1">Dr. Carie Perrino</h1>
            <p class="hero-el text-sm text-terracotta font-semibold mb-4">NMD, RDN, CLT &middot; Co-Founder</p>

            <div class="hero-el flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
              <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Gut Health</span>
              <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Mold Illness</span>
              <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Hormones</span>
              <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Nutrition</span>
            </div>

            <p class="hero-el text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Dr. Carie's own battle with IBS led her to naturopathic medicine. A registered dietitian turned NMD, she brings rare dual expertise to every patient. She's now faculty at Sonoran University, teaching the next generation of naturopathic doctors.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-el flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-3">
              <a href="/book" class="magnetic-btn cta-shine group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-sage hover:bg-sage-dark text-white font-bold text-sm px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-sage/25 overflow-hidden">
                <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2">
                  Book with Dr. Perrino
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                </span>
              </a>
              <a href="tel:+14809140521" class="magnetic-btn relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white hover:bg-sage-pale text-charcoal font-bold text-sm px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md border border-sage-pale/60 overflow-hidden">
                Call (480) 914-0521
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== 2. THEIR STORY ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[60rem] h-[60rem] rounded-full bg-sage-pale/20 blur-[140px] -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-10 scroll-reveal">
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-terracotta mb-4">Her story</p>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal">
          Her own health journey led her to <span class="text-sage">change&nbsp;medicine.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
        <div class="scroll-reveal space-y-5">
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-text-light leading-relaxed">
            Dr. Carie knows firsthand what it feels like to be dismissed by doctors. For years, she struggled with IBS and chronic digestive issues that no conventional doctor could adequately explain or treat. That frustration became the catalyst for her entire career.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-text-light leading-relaxed">
            She began her path in nutrition science, earning a Bachelor of Science in Nutritional Sciences from the University of Missouri and becoming a Registered Dietitian Nutritionist. But she wanted to do more than advise on diet &mdash; she wanted to get to the root of why her patients were sick in the first place.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-text-light leading-relaxed">
            That drive led her to Sonoran University of Health Sciences, where she earned her naturopathic medical degree. Today, Dr. Carie holds the rare combination of being both an NMD and an RDN &mdash; giving her unparalleled expertise in the intersection of nutrition and medicine. She serves as faculty at Sonoran University, teaching nutrition, IV therapy, and medical ethics to the next generation of naturopathic doctors.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="scroll-reveal bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-8 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm" style="transition-delay: 0.12s;">
          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-5">Education</p>

          <div class="space-y-0">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-sage ring-[3px] ring-sage/20 mt-1.5"></div>
                <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-sage-pale/60 min-h-6"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="pb-5">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">BS Nutritional Sciences</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-text-light">University of Missouri (Mizzou)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-terracotta ring-[3px] ring-terracotta/20 mt-1.5"></div>
                <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-sage-pale/60 min-h-6"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="pb-5">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">Registered Dietitian Nutritionist</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-text-light">RDN Credential</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-sage ring-[3px] ring-sage/20 mt-1.5"></div>
                <div class="w-px flex-1 bg-sage-pale/60 min-h-6"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="pb-5">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">Naturopathic Medical Degree</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-text-light">Sonoran University of Health Sciences</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center shrink-0">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-terracotta ring-[3px] ring-terracotta/20 mt-1.5"></div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-charcoal">Faculty Appointment</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-text-light">Sonoran University</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr class="mt-8 mb-6 border-sage-pale/40" />

          <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-4">Credentials</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Sonoran Faculty</span>
            <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Registered Dietitian</span>
            <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">CLT</span>
            <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">Co-Founder</span>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-[#F5E0D0] rounded-xl p-4 mt-5">
            <p class="text-xs text-charcoal leading-relaxed">
              <span class="font-bold">Fun fact:</span> Dr. Carie was recently featured in VoyagePhoenix for her work in naturopathic medicine. She teaches the next generation of naturopathic doctors while continuing to see patients full-time.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== 3. SPECIALTIES ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-[#F5E0D0] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] rounded-full bg-white/15 blur-[120px] translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/4 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-10 scroll-reveal">
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-terracotta mb-4">Areas of expertise</p>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal">
          Where Dr. Perrino makes the <span class="text-sage">biggest&nbsp;impact.</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-7 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sage icon-search" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-charcoal mb-2">Gut Health & Digestive Disorders</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">As someone who battled IBS herself, Dr. Carie understands digestive issues on a deeply personal level. She runs comprehensive stool testing, SIBO breath tests, and food sensitivity panels to get to the real cause of your symptoms.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">IBS</span>
            <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">SIBO</span>
            <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Leaky Gut</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-7 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300" style="transition-delay: 0.06s;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-terracotta/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-terracotta icon-zap" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-charcoal mb-2">Mold Illness & Environmental Toxins</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Chronic fatigue, brain fog, and mysterious symptoms that no one can explain? Dr. Carie specializes in identifying and treating mold toxicity and environmental illness with evidence-based protocols.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Mycotoxins</span>
            <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Brain Fog</span>
            <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Chronic Fatigue</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-7 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300" style="transition-delay: 0.12s;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sage icon-heartbeat" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-charcoal mb-2">Hormonal Balance</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">From thyroid dysfunction to menopause and everything in between, Dr. Carie evaluates the full hormonal picture and uses nutrition as a foundational tool in her treatment plans.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Thyroid</span>
            <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Menopause</span>
            <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Adrenals</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="scroll-reveal bento-tilt bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] p-7 border border-sage-pale/40 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300" style="transition-delay: 0.18s;">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-terracotta/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-terracotta icon-nod" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-charcoal mb-2">Clinical Nutrition</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-4">With dual credentials as an NMD and RDN, Dr. Carie approaches nutrition differently. She creates evidence-based dietary protocols that address specific conditions, not just generic meal plans.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Medical Nutrition</span>
            <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">IV Nutrition</span>
            <span class="bg-terracotta/10 text-terracotta text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Supplementation</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== 4. MEET OTHER DOCTORS ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-cream relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-[40rem] h-[40rem] rounded-full bg-sage-pale/20 blur-[120px] translate-x-1/4 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 scroll-reveal">
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-sage mb-4">The rest of your team</p>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-charcoal mb-3">
          Your care is always a <span class="text-sage">team&nbsp;effort.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-light max-w-lg mx-auto">Every patient benefits from the combined expertise of all three doctors.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/doctors/dr-warren" class="scroll-reveal group bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col sm:flex-row border border-sage-pale/40">
          <div class="sm:w-40 shrink-0"><img src="/images/doctors/spencer-headshot.jpg" alt="Dr. Spencer Warren" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top aspect-[4/3] sm:aspect-auto sm:min-h-[200px]" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="p-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <p class="text-lg font-black text-charcoal mb-1 group-hover:text-sage transition-colors">Dr. Spencer Warren</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-sage font-semibold mb-2">NMD &middot; Co-Founder</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">ASU magna cum laude, Mayo Clinic trained. Specializes in fertility, GI health, and cardiovascular wellness.</p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-sage">Meet Dr. Warren <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/doctors/dr-newman" class="scroll-reveal group bg-white rounded-[1.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col sm:flex-row border border-sage-pale/40" style="transition-delay: 0.08s;">
          <div class="sm:w-40 shrink-0"><img src="/images/doctors/bailey-headshot.jpeg" alt="Dr. Bailey Newman" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top aspect-[4/3] sm:aspect-auto sm:min-h-[200px]" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="p-6 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <p class="text-lg font-black text-charcoal mb-1 group-hover:text-sage transition-colors">Dr. Bailey Newman</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-earth font-semibold mb-2">NMD</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed mb-3">Bilingual naturopathic doctor specializing in digestive health, women's health, and acupuncture.</p>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-sage">Meet Dr. Newman <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== 5. CTA ==================== -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-[#1a2516] relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-sage/6 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/4" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-sage/4 translate-y-1/3 -translate-x-1/4" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container-main relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto scroll-reveal">
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-terracotta-light mb-4">Ready to start?</p>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem)] font-black leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-white mb-5">
          Book your visit with <span class="text-sage-light">Dr.&nbsp;Perrino.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">Ready to work with a doctor who truly understands gut health from the inside out? Dr. Carie is accepting new patients.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/book" class="magnetic-btn cta-shine group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-sage hover:bg-sage-dark text-white font-bold text-sm px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-sage/25 overflow-hidden">
            <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-2">Book with Dr. Perrino <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></span>
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+14809140521" class="magnetic-btn relative inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/8 hover:bg-white/15 text-white font-bold text-sm px-8 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 border border-white/15 overflow-hidden">Call (480) 914-0521</a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/40 mt-5">No referral needed &middot; 75-90 min first visit &middot; Tempe or virtual</p>
      </div>
